## Stash plugin rules

- Structure
  - Manifest: [stash-plugin/automate-stash.yml](mdc:stash-plugin/automate-stash.yml)
  - Main scripts: [stash-plugin/automate-stash-enhanced.js](mdc:stash-plugin/automate-stash-enhanced.js), [stash-plugin/automate-stash-compact.js](mdc:stash-plugin/automate-stash-compact.js)
  - Styles: [stash-plugin/automate-stash.css](mdc:stash-plugin/automate-stash.css)
  - Debug helpers: [stash-plugin/debug-edit-panel-enhanced.js](mdc:stash-plugin/debug-edit-panel-enhanced.js)

- Guidelines
  - Do not use GM_* APIs; rely on Stash/plugin facilities
  - Keep UI/UX consistent with userscripts where feasible
  - Validate selectors against the Stash UI; maintain fallbacks

- Install & troubleshooting
  - Follow [stash-plugin/INSTALLATION.md](mdc:stash-plugin/INSTALLATION.md) and [stash-plugin/TROUBLESHOOTING.md](mdc:stash-plugin/TROUBLESHOOTING.md)

